As an UNLUCKY girl prepares to face her death, an UNDEAD who desperately wants to die appears before her! Vicious, violent and buck naked! An unprecedented picaresque hero appears in Shonen Jump!
(Source: MANGA Plus)
Winner of Tsugimanga 2020 Award in the Manga Category.
Kono Subarashii Sekai ni Shukufuku wo! Fantastic Days

The modern world is one of diversity, where "genjins" live together with humans. At Keiki High School, where many genjins attend, a human boy, Yutaka Shinsou, enrolls there. Yutaka, who often goes along with other people's wishes instead of expressing his own feelings, meets a werewolf girl, Tsumiki Ogami. With Tsumiki, he has a feeling that he'll finally be able to be himself...... A new-normal story about two people's coming-of-age!

(Source: Sunday Webry, translated) Note: - Ranked 3rd place in the Tsugimanga 2024 Award in the Print Manga Category.
Tokidoki Bosotto Russiago de Dereru Tonari no Alya-san

Masachika Kuse sits next to Alya, a girl of Russian and Japanese descent. She's beautiful, haughty, and an exceptional student, while Masachika is nerdy and known for being a slacker. He's an easy target for her comments in Russian, which she's all too happy to translate—except he can understand what she's really saying!
(Source: K Manga)
